  "2340870": {
    "name": "Rugby 25",
    "steam_appid": 2340870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/b7c376f1dbf6add864e583c9514238e5.poster.avif?t=1764149742\" width=614 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/b7c376f1dbf6add864e583c9514238e5.webm?t=1764149742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/b7c376f1dbf6add864e583c9514238e5.mp4?t=1764149742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><strong>Rugby 25 带你沉浸于前所未有的橄榄球视频游戏世界，感受极速冲刺体验。</strong> 从本地俱乐部的激烈对决到盛大的国际锦标赛，每一次精准的传球、每一次成功的擒抱摔倒、每一次勇敢的尝试，都完美展现了橄榄球运动的精髓。逼真的游戏玩法、深度的战略布局以及令人血脉喷张的动作瞬间，让你感受到指尖跃动的力量。准备踏上一段难忘的旅程吧，因为每一场比赛都是一场鏖战，而每一次胜利都是你通往传奇道路上的宝贵收获。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有史以来最全面的橄榄球视频游戏：</h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/3e2a125355556eedbdf7f46f5594da7e.poster.avif?t=1764149742\" width=614 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/3e2a125355556eedbdf7f46f5594da7e.webm?t=1764149742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/3e2a125355556eedbdf7f46f5594da7e.mp4?t=1764149742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><strong>在 Rugby 25 中，体验橄榄球游戏终极对决的激情！</strong> 踏上法兰西体育场 (Stade de France)、安联球场 (Allianz Stadium, London) 体育场等传奇球场的神圣草坪，争夺橄榄球界的霸主地位。你将与超过 140 支国际球队一较高下，包括新西兰、南非、英格兰、爱尔兰、法国和澳大利亚等橄榄球强国球队，以及来自 11 个顶级联赛的 150 多支劲旅，涵盖 URC、英格兰超级联赛、法国 Top 14、MLR、超级橄榄球联赛以及六国锦标赛。<br><br>无论你是指挥国家队还是领导顶级俱乐部，挑选最全面的球队阵容，在橄榄球世界最具标志性的球场任意驰骋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/258875965bb11d28b24781aa2a574807.poster.avif?t=1764149742\" width=614 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/258875965bb11d28b24781aa2a574807.webm?t=1764149742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/258875965bb11d28b24781aa2a574807.mp4?t=1764149742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >踏上橄榄球世界的璀璨舞台：</h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/47e5980860bbb5e2fbade6e02694d6fc.poster.avif?t=1764149742\" width=614 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/47e5980860bbb5e2fbade6e02694d6fc.webm?t=1764149742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/47e5980860bbb5e2fbade6e02694d6fc.mp4?t=1764149742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><strong>在本地和线上展开激烈对决。</strong> Rugby 25 以逼真的物理效果和动态球员动画为你呈现真实的比赛强度。挑战并战胜你的朋友，或与全球线上和跨平台的对手一决高下，在多种游戏模式中追逐胜利，包括一次性友谊赛和紧张刺激的竞争性赛事。<br><br>在世界舞台上展现你的技能，攀登排行榜，主宰球场，证明你就是 Rugby 25 的终极冠军！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >铸就橄榄球的传奇：</h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/bfa23d7da8f4c49652464d69eb35418d.poster.avif?t=1764149742\" width=614 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/bfa23d7da8f4c49652464d69eb35418d.webm?t=1764149742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/bfa23d7da8f4c49652464d69eb35418d.mp4?t=1764149742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><strong>在 Rugby 25 中，建立、管理和领导你的梦之队，共同追逐荣耀。</strong> 在 Rugby 25 职业模式中，体验职业教练生涯的跌宕起伏和挑战重重，你的每一个决定都将影响成败。训练球员、制定获胜策略，并在铸就橄榄球传奇的道路上智取对手。<br><br>在 Rugby 25 学院中释放创造力！设计自己的球员、球队、球衣和体育场，在你的球场上自豪地展示独特的标志和颜色。将你的愿景变为现实，并与全世界分享你的创意作品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/1c07a04ed482fedae39ec982737b3b91.poster.avif?t=1764149742\" width=614 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/1c07a04ed482fedae39ec982737b3b91.webm?t=1764149742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340870/extras/1c07a04ed482fedae39ec982737b3b91.mp4?t=1764149742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
